* General
  > {https://github.com/OpenVPN/easy-rsa}[repo]

  PKI tooling developed by openvpn.

  Holds all data in a directory.

** Files
   - `ca.crt` - CA cert
   - `vars` - easyrsa and org configurations
   - `index.txt` - cert index

** Subdirs
   - `private` - private keys
   - `reqs` - sertificate requests
   - `revoked` - revoked certs
   - `inline` - inline files for certs
   - `issued` - issued certs
